{
  "cli": {
    "version": ">= 12.0.0",
    "appVersionSource": "remote"
  },
  "build": {
    "_comments": [
      "Three profiles in increasing strictness: development → preview → production.",
      "Each layer adds a constraint:",
      "  - development: dev-client APK with developmentClient=true; you can",
      "    attach Metro to it and iterate without a rebuild.",
      "  - preview: internal distribution APK/IPA, production-style bundle",
      "    but pointed at a non-prod API and signed with a non-store cert so",
      "    we can hand it to QA.",
      "  - production: store-bound IPA/AAB. Reads release-mode env vars and",
      "    uploads to TestFlight / Play Internal via `eas submit`.",
      "EXPO_PUBLIC_API_BASE_URL is consumed by src/lib/env.ts; falls back to",
      "localhost when unset (dev convenience).",
      "EXPO_PUBLIC_SENTRY_DSN gates the Sentry init in src/lib/monitoring.ts."
    ],
    "development": {
      "developmentClient": true,
      "distribution": "internal",
      "channel": "development",
      "env": {
        "EXPO_PUBLIC_API_BASE_URL": "http://localhost:28333"
      },
      "android": {
        "buildType": "apk",
        "gradleCommand": ":app:assembleDebug"
      },
      "ios": {
        "buildConfiguration": "Debug"
      }
    },
    "preview": {
      "distribution": "internal",
      "channel": "preview",
      "env": {
        "EXPO_PUBLIC_API_BASE_URL": "https://api-staging.preodds.example",
        "EXPO_PUBLIC_SENTRY_DSN": ""
      },
      "android": {
        "buildType": "apk",
        "gradleCommand": ":app:assembleRelease"
      },
      "ios": {
        "buildConfiguration": "Release"
      }
    },
    "production": {
      "distribution": "store",
      "channel": "production",
      "autoIncrement": true,
      "env": {
        "EXPO_PUBLIC_API_BASE_URL": "https://api.preodds.example",
        "EXPO_PUBLIC_SENTRY_DSN": ""
      },
      "android": {
        "buildType": "app-bundle"
      },
      "ios": {
        "buildConfiguration": "Release"
      }
    }
  },
  "submit": {
    "production": {
      "_comments": [
        "Fill these via `eas secret:create`:",
        "  ASC_APP_ID, ASC_APPLE_ID for iOS",
        "  GOOGLE_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_KEY for Android",
        "Don't commit credentials — eas.json is checked in."
      ],
      "ios": {
        "ascAppId": "${ASC_APP_ID}",
        "appleTeamId": "${APPLE_TEAM_ID}"
      },
      "android": {
        "track": "internal"
      }
    }
  }
}
